OL,5, About 15 million more people in England
OL,6, could be prescribed daily              
OL,7, cholesterol-lowering statin pills to   
OL,8, cut their risk of heart attacks and    
OL,9, stroke, new advice for the NHS says.   
OL,11,FGiven the very cheap price of the      
OL,12,Ftablets and the possible health gains, 
OL,13,Fthey should be considered more often,  
OL,14,Fthe draft guidance says.               
OL,16,FThere can be side effects though.      
OL,18,FThere is debate about how widely this  
OL,19,Flong-term treatment should be given and
OL,20,Fwhat associated risks are acceptable.  
